# Feature: Quiz Suggestion Logic

## Purpose
Suggest a project idea based on a user's quiz responses and selected filters.

## API Route
**POST** `/api/quiz/suggest`

## Request Body
```json
{
  "answers": 
  "filters": {
    "difficulty": "easy|medium|hard",
    "vibe": "creative|useful|silly",
    "tech": "string",
    "time": "string"
  }
}